{"tid":518730,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"點面對衰上司","createTime":"2018-01-03T15:41:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-04T13:07:54.000Z","uid":87428,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"386584d1f42c101086cf740a13851be6b068d3b6","tid":518730,"uid":87428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T15:41:38.000Z","msg":"見你唔出聲 沒造化<br />\n唔識擦鞋 <br />\n就咩都俾你做 甚至對你指指點點<br />\n單單打打<br />\n<br />\n反佢 唔做 但佢目標可能就係想踢你走<br />\n咁你就益左佢<br />\n<br />\n唔反 日日玩你 多野做 遲收工<br />\n話你做錯野 重做<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 頂硬上<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 立即請辭"},{"pid":"b59499e4130754f0f0ca5d0b4105211decec08a3","tid":518730,"uid":60000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"386584d1f42c101086cf740a13851be6b068d3b6","tid":518730,"uid":87428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T15:41:38.000Z","msg":"見你唔出聲 沒造化<br />\n唔識擦鞋 <br />\n就咩都俾你做 甚至對你指指點點<br />\n單單打打<br />\n<br />\n反佢 唔做 但佢目標可能就係想踢你走<br />\n咁你就益左佢<br />\n<br />\n唔反 日日玩你 多野做 遲收工<br />\n話你做錯野 重做<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 頂硬上<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 立即請辭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T04:44:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e6347c9d3d1eec657f82cd58071be4e5564251b","tid":518730,"uid":69206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T08:30:50.000Z","msg":"請辭之前：<br />\n<br />\n1、辭職前儲定衰上司做錯嘢嘅證據，預備發俾更高嘅管理層（just in case）。離職時放少少風出去其實你知道佢做錯乜乜乜，keep咗email。呢啲一定要係大錯或係integrity嘅問題（番工遲到唔算）。等佢知佢有痛腳喺你手，唔好玩嘢。<br />\n<br />\n2、搵吓有冇高層同你關係ok，臨走前自己作定complementary letter，請佢簽。<br />\n<br />\n3、referee嘅contact唔好寫衰上司，寫關係良好之高層（HR, GM呢類也可）"},{"pid":"2276e37c0c387b11e3380968ccff5d5bf8f5a4c8","tid":518730,"uid":15208,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"386584d1f42c101086cf740a13851be6b068d3b6","tid":5